    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but i've been reading a lot about how much it's needed for the climate goals the city has. do most urban planners actually see it as a viable way to hit those carbon targets, or is it just one of those things that sounds good on paper but doesn't really work?",
      "source": "evaluator"
